snippet.textDisplay: Why don't who just quarantined all world for 14 days? If only they do it from the beginning, it would be no covid 19 now. Close all borders except for those countries that had zero covid. I think those countries who had covid would eventually try their best to recover, and other would have more ability to help by doing so.
